Package: thermokarstdetection
Title: Detect Thermokarst from Elevation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Heidi",
           family = "Rodenhizer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hgr7@nau.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5824-3302"))
Description: Detect thermokarst features in permafrost terrain from a single digital terrain model. This function compares each cells elevation to a circular neighborhood median elevation to detect cells which are lower than the surrounding landscape.
